cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper discusses a new variant of hierarchical clustering, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the lack of evaluation methods and benchmark data, which suggests that it may belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.DB (Databases). Additionally, the paper discusses the theoretical analysis of generation parameters, which suggests that it may belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper includes experiments with visualisation tools, which suggests that it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
